{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01EwjbNW9Ly8cpjwhFHhgNsH","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me plan the full migration. The key challenge is replacing Quarkus-specific features:\n\n1. **Panache** (active record pattern) → Standard JPA with `EntityManager`\n2. **Qute templates** (`{#include base}`, `{msg:...}`, `@CheckedTemplate`) → JSP with JSTL\n3. **Quarkus REST** (`@ServerExceptionMapper`) → Standard JAX-RS `ExceptionMapper`\n4. **`@Blocking`** → Not needed in standard Jakarta EE\n5. **`@TemplateExtension`** → No longer needed (handled in JSP)\n6. **`@MessageBundle`** → Standard `ResourceBundle`\n\nI'll use WildFly as the Jakarta EE runtime. Let me now execute the migration. I'll do this systematically:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":500,"cache_read_input_tokens":65800,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":500,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1434},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c7f97aa4-1c2c-44bf-80a1-31ac11b107ff","uuid":"8e9f6885-bf57-4e38-999d-a1532b488e77"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01EwjbNW9Ly8cpjwhFHhgNsH","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01WrcZrpvJCzhM3Uf2Twf4oq","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/pom.xml","content":"<?xml version=\"1.0\"?>\n<project xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 https://maven.apache.org/xsd/maven-4.0.0.xsd\"\n         xmlns=\"http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0\"\n         xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\">\n  <modelVersion>4.0.0</modelVersion>\n  <groupId>org.jakarta.samples.petclinic</groupId>\n  <artifactId>jakarta-petclinic</artifactId>\n  <version>1.0.0-SNAPSHOT</version>\n  <packaging>war</packaging>\n\n  <properties>\n    <compiler-plugin.version>3.14.0</compiler-plugin.version>\n    <maven.compiler.source>21</maven.compiler.source>\n    <maven.compiler.target>21</maven.compiler.target>\n    <project.build.sourceEncoding>UTF-8</project.build.sourceEncoding>\n    <project.reporting.outputEncoding>UTF-8</project.reporting.outputEncoding>\n    <war-plugin.version>3.4.0</war-plugin.version>\n    <jakartaee.version>10.0.0</jakartaee.version>\n    <webjars-bootstrap.version>5.1.3</webjars-bootstrap.version>\n    <webjars-font-awesome.version>4.7.0</webjars-font-awesome.version>\n    <jackson.version>2.17.2</jackson.version>\n  </properties>\n\n  <dependencies>\n    <!-- Jakarta EE 10 API -->\n    <dependency>\n      <groupId>jakarta.platform</groupId>\n      <artifactId>jakarta.jakartaee-api</artifactId>\n      <version>${jakartaee.version}</version>\n      <scope>provided</scope>\n    </dependency>\n\n    <!-- Jackson for JSON serialization -->\n    <dependency>\n      <groupId>com.fasterxml.jackson.core</groupId>\n      <artifactId>jackson-databind</artifactId>\n      <version>${jackson.version}</version>\n    </dependency>\n   