{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01M6dv254ajHmvtrYmjSfMD6","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks are complete. Here's a summary of the migration:\n\n## Migration Complete: Quarkus -> Jakarta EE\n\n**Result: 15/15 smoke tests passing**\n\n### What was done:\n- **Build**: Rewrote `pom.xml` from Quarkus to standard Maven WAR packaging with Jakarta EE 10 dependencies\n- **Runtime**: WildFly 35.0.1.Final with JDK 21 (replacing Quarkus runtime)\n- **Entities**: Replaced Quarkus Panache active record pattern with standard JPA `@Entity` classes with `EntityManager` injection\n- **Controllers**: Replaced Quarkus REST `@Path` resources with `@WebServlet` servlets for HTML pages + JAX-RS `@Path` for JSON APIs\n- **Templates**: Replaced Qute template engine with JSP + JSTL\n- **Transactions**: Used `UserTransaction` for manual transaction management (CDI `@Transactional` unreliable on servlet methods)\n- **Data Init**: Replaced `import.sql` with `@Singleton @Startup` CDI bean\n- **Config**: Created `persistence.xml`, `web.xml`, `beans.xml`, WildFly CLI datasource config\n- **Docker**: Multi-stage build with proper permission handling\n\n### Key issues resolved:\n1. curl-minimal conflict on WildFly UBI image\n2. WildFly CLI semicolon parsing in H2 JDBC URL\n3. JSP EL requiring JavaBean getters on entity classes\n4. File permission issues (root vs jboss user)\n5. `@Transactional` interceptor not working on servlet methods -> `UserTransaction`"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":558,"cache_read_input_tokens":94829,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":558,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":398},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c7f97aa4-1c2c-44bf-80a1-31ac11b107ff","uuid":"4730133b-e4ac-4f70-961c-d1eb6bf67c49"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":1646837,"duration_api_ms":1704215,"num_turns":213,"result":"All tasks are complete. Here's a summary of the migration:\n\n## Migration Complete: Quarkus -> Jakarta EE\n\n**Result: 15/15 smoke tests passing**\n\n### What was done:\n- **Build**: Rewrote `pom.xml` from Quarkus to standard Maven WAR packaging with Jakarta EE 10 dependencies\n- **Runtime**: WildFly 35.0.1.Final with JDK 21 (replacing Quarkus runtime)\n- **Entities**: Replaced Quarkus Panache active record pattern with standard JPA `@Entity` classes with `EntityManager` injection\n- **Controllers**: Replaced Quarkus REST `@Path` resources with `@WebServlet` servlets for HTML pages + JAX-RS `@Path` for JSON APIs\n- **Templates**: Replaced Qute template engine with JSP + JSTL\n- **Transactions**: Used `UserTransaction` for manual transaction management (CDI `@Transactional` unreliable on servlet methods)\n- **Data Init**: Replaced `import.sql` with `@Singleton @Startup` CDI bean\n- **Config**: Created `persistence.xml`, `web.xml`, `beans.xml`, WildFly CLI datasource config\n- **Docker**: Multi-stage build with proper permission handling\n\n### Key issues resolved:\n1. curl-minimal conflict on WildFly UBI image\n2. WildFly CLI semicolon parsing in H2 JDBC URL\n3. JSP EL requiring JavaBean getters on entity classes\n4. File permission issues (root vs jboss user)\n5. `@Transactional` interceptor not working on servlet methods -> `UserTransaction`","session_id":"c7f97aa4-1c2c-44bf-80a1-31ac11b107ff","total_cost_usd":29.173023590000025,"usage":{"input_tokens":129,"cache_creation_input_tokens":220479,"cache_read_input_tokens":10617309,"output_tokens":76152,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":220479}},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929":{"inputTokens":520,"outputTokens":169,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreat